    "description": "Rich chocolate cake with a molten center that oozes when cut. Perfect dessert for chocolate lovers or special occasions like birthdays or romantic dinners.",
    "content": "Rich chocolate cake with a molten center that oozes when cut. Perfect dessert for chocolate lovers or special occasions like birthdays or romantic dinners.\r\n## Ingredients\r\nDark chocolate\r\nButter\r\nSugar\r\nEggs\r\nFlour\r\nVanilla extract\r\nSalt\r\n## Steps\r\nMelt the chocolate and butter together over low heat until smooth.\r\nWhisk eggs and sugar in a separate bowl until creamy and pale.\r\nFold the chocolate mixture gently into the eggs, then add flour and salt.\r\nPour the batter into prepared ramekins and bake until edges are firm but centers are soft.\r\nRemove from oven and let cool slightly before serving.\r\nCut into the center to reveal the molten chocolate and enjoy immediately.",
