    "title": "Crispy Chicken Burger",
    "description": "Golden, crispy chicken fillet on a soft bun with lettuce, pickles, and sauce. Perfect for a quick, satisfying meal or lunch with friends.",
    "content": "## Ingredients\r\nChicken fillet\r\nFlour\r\nEgg\r\nBread crumbs\r\nLettuce\r\nPickles\r\nBurger bun\r\nMayonnaise or sauce\r\n## Steps\r\nCoat chicken in flour, dip in egg, and cover with bread crumbs.\r\nFry until golden and crispy.\r\nPlace chicken fillet on a toasted bun.\r\nAdd lettuce, pickles, and sauce of your choice.\r\nServe immediately while crispy for maximum flavor.",
