    "title": "Chewy Choc-Chip Cookies",
    "description": "Soft, chewy cookies packed with chocolate chips. Perfect snack or dessert for any time, especially with a glass of milk.",
    "content": "Soft, chewy cookies packed with chocolate chips. Perfect snack or dessert for any time, especially with a glass of milk.\r\n## Ingredients\r\nFlour\r\nButter\r\nSugar\r\nEggs\r\nChocolate chips\r\nVanilla extract\r\nBaking soda\r\nSalt\r\n## Steps\r\nCream butter and sugar together until light.\r\nAdd eggs and vanilla extract, mixing well.\r\nFold in flour, baking soda, salt, and chocolate chips.\r\nScoop dough onto a baking tray.\r\nBake until edges are golden and centers remain soft.\r\nCool slightly and serve.",
